skinparam shadowing false
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam linetype ortho
left to right direction

title localization.launch.py per-node topic directions

legend right
Direction is from each node's perspective.
IN = subscribes/listens, OUT = publishes, IN/OUT = both.
endlegend

component "ekf_map\n(robot_localization/ekf_node)" as ekf

note right of ekf
|= Topic |= Dir |
| /wheel/odom | IN |
| /imu/data | IN |
| /tag_global_pose | IN |
| /tf_static | IN |
| /tf | IN/OUT |
| /odometry/filtered | OUT |
end note

@enduml
